          "Logan Boese"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You always loved animals. In life you were a very good vet tech. You loved your job and loved the animals . In the line of duty you saw the good and the bad. And as such learned just what kind of monsters humans could be. Now that you are a “real” monster, you decided it was time to turn the tables. It is your mission to make others see what you do when you look at the creatures of the urban wilderness."
        ],
