        [
          "You have figured out that few people in this Camarilla respect Nosferatu - and by extension the urban landscape - and you want to change that. Make your clan a force to be reconned with."
        ],
        [
          "Your animals have been complaining about development and city ordinances that have harmed them, all in the name of gentrification. Work those in power to try and ensure they are taken care of."
        ],
